==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Labor-saving
<hw>La"bor-sav`ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Saving labor;
adapted to supersede or diminish the labor of men; designed to replace
or conserve human and especially manual labor; <as>as,
<ex>labor-saving</ex> machinery; <ex>labor-saving</ex> appliances{4};
<ex>labor-saving</ex> devices like washing machines</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> laborsaving.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> + <source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Laborsome</ent>⟦br⟧
